A%20Ukrainian%20combat%20medic%20who%20requested%20anonymity%20due%20to%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20work%20she%20does%20told%20BI%20the%20struggle%20to%20quickly%20evacuate%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20problem%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20only%20worsened%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-behind-80-russia-frontline-casualties-report-nyt-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrones%20becoming%20more%20prolific%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20a%20totally%20different%20war%20from%20what%20is%20going%20on%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20handling%20a%20drone%20on%20a%20stand%20in%20a%20field.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a25d00dfb1341e9fef2b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20military%20operating%20a%20Punisher%20drone.%3Cp%3ELibkos%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%201%20million%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20or%20injured%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20with%20casualties%20stemming%20heavily%20from%20drones%20and%20artillery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheap%20drones%20swarming%20the%20skies%20over%20Ukraine's%20battlefields%20can%20severely%20delay%20medical%20evacuations.%20The%20drones%20serve%20as%20aerial%20eyes%20for%20artillery%2C%20bombers%20that%20can%20drop%20grenades%2C%20and%20precision-strike%20munitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20medic%20said%20Russian%20troops%20target%20vehicles%20known%20to%20be%20carrying%20out%20evacuations%2C%20a%20war%20crime%20about%20which%20other%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20repeatedly%20raised%20concerns%20in%20this%20war.%20Russia%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbakhmut-how-ukraine-lost-city-russia-won-hollow-victory-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaim%20for%20the%20combat%20medics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20said%2C%20because%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20kill%20a%20medic%2C%20it%20means%20that%20you%20killed%20thousands%20of%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20all%20the%20people%20they%20might%20have%20saved%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20special%20or%20different%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20attract%20a%20drone%2C%26quot%3B%20Tango%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20goes%20especially%20for%20evac%2C%20and%20they%20specifically%20target%20medical%20vehicles%20or%20anybody%20with%20a%20backpack.%20You%20never%20wear%20a%20medic%20patch%20on%20the%20front%20line.%20That's%20a%20guaranteed%20drone%20strike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20are%20only%20one%20of%20the%20war's%20many%20causes%20of%20bodily%20harm%20and%20death.%20A%202023%20medical%20study%20found%20that%2070%25%20of%20Ukrainian%20war%20injuries%20were%20caused%20by%20shelling%20or%20rocket%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Graves%20are%20seen%20in%20a%20misty%20graveyard%2C%20with%20Ukrainian%20flags%2C%20candles%2C%20and%20flowers%20on%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6755e6d9a57635a3d24d0281%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGraves%20at%20the%20Lychakiv%20cemetery%20in%20Lviv%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20of%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20killed%20since%20Russia%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMykola%20Tys%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20medic%20said%20first%20responders%20sometimes%20reach%20injured%20soldiers%20quickly%20but%20can't%20evacuate%20if%20nearby%20roads%20are%20controlled%20by%20Russians%20or%20exposed%20to%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20can%20mean%20waiting%20hours%20or%20even%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExtended%20delays%20in%20crucial