%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20travelled%20to%20Vietnam%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20said%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20had%20flown%20abroad%20to%20party%20on%20New%20Year%20while%20the%20nation%20was%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20veteran%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh.%20Hitting%20back%2C%20Congress%20MP%20B%20Manickam%20Tagore%20has%20questioned%20why%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20private%20travel%20bothers%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20and%20the%20counter-attack%20are%20playing%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20massive%20political%20row%20surrounding%20the%20cremation%20of%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20had%20humiliated%20Dr%20Singh%20by%20organising%20the%20cremation%20at%20Nigambodh%20Ghat.%20The%20BJP%20has%20trashed%20these%20allegations%20and%20said%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20had%20provided%20a%20state%20funeral%20to%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20done%20everything%20required%20to%20honour%20his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20heated%20row%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20trip%20gave%20the%20BJP%20fresh%20ammo%20to%20target%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Shehzad%20Poonawalla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20is%20in%20mourning.%20The%20government%20has%20announced%20seven%20days%20of%20national%20mourning.%20As%20expected%20from%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20we%20have%20received%20information%20that%20he%20has%20left%20for%20tourism%20and%20to%20party.%20You%20will%20remember%20that%20after%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%20on%20Mumbai%2C%20newspapers%20had%20reported%20how%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20partied%20all%20night.%20And%20today%2C%20he%20does%20not%20care%20about%20honouring%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh.%20He%20just%20wants%20to%20play%20politics%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202008%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20multiple%20reports%20had%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20then%2038%2C%20partied%20all%20night%20at%20a%20farmhouse%20on%20Delhi's%20outskirts%20to%20celebrate%20his%20friend%20Samir%20Sharma's%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Tagore%20countered%20the%20BJP's%20charge%20and%20termed%20it%20%26quot%3Btake%20diversion%26quot%3B%20politics.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20will%20the%20Sanghis%20stop%20this%20'Take%20Diversion'%20politics%3F%20The%20way%20Modi%20denied%20Dr%20Saheb%20a%20place%20for%20cremation%20on%20the%20Yamuna%20banks%20and%20how%20his%20ministers%20cornered%20Dr%20Saheb's%20family%20is%20shameful.%20If%20Mr%20Gandhi%20travel%20privately%2C%20why%20does%20it%20bother%20you%3F%C2%A0Get%20well%20in%20New%20Year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Virudhunagar%20MP%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Tariq%20Anwar%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20trip%20was%20pre-planned.%20%26quot%3BHe%20paid%20his%20tribute%20to%20Dr%20Singh%20and%20was%20present%20during%20the%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20IANS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Poonawalla%20also%20said%20top%20Congress%20leaders%20were%20missing%20when%20the%20ashes%20of%20Dr%20Singh%20were%20being%20immersed%20in%20the%20Yamuna.%20%26quot%3BNo%20Congress%20leader%20was%20present%20there%2C%20none%20from%20the%20first%20family.%20If%20someone%20insulted%20Dr%20Singh%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20and%20Gandhi%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20party%20leaders%20skipped%20the%20ashes%20immersion%20to%20give%20privacy%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20felt%20that%20since%20the%20family%20did%20not%20get%20any%20privacy%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20cremation%20and%20some%20extended%20family%20members%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20pyre%20site%2C%20it%20would%20be%20appropriate%20to%20give%20them%20some%20privacy%20for%20the%20Phool%20Chunana%20and%20the%20immersion%2