ttle%2C%20and%20before%20I%20knew%20it%2C%20I%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-am-the-youngest-president-of-mothers-against-drunk-driving-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebehind%20the%20wheel%2C%20drunk%20and%20reckless%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20crashed%20my%20car%20that%20night.%20Thankfully%2C%20no%20one%20was%20hurt%2C%20but%20the%20fallout%20hit%20me%20like%20a%20tidal%20wave.%20In%20the%20hospital%20afterward%2C%20I%20wasn't%20thinking%20about%20the%20damage%20to%20my%20car%20or%20the%20legal%20consequences%20%E2%80%94%20all%20I%20could%20think%20about%20was%20my%20son%20Neil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c52f5a5c-6556-4ae7-9d35-fe68b2801d08%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20the%20dad%20I%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20coming%20to%20the%20painful%20conclusion%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20father%20I%20had%20become.%20The%20kind%20who%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-ai-app-for-bedtime-stories-for-my-kids-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emissed%20bedtime%20stories%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20because%20he%20was%20desperate%20for%20a%20drink.%20The%20kind%20who%20made%20promises%20to%20take%20his%20son%20on%20trips%20and%20just%20as%20quickly%20broke%20those%20promises%20when%20the%20urge%20to%20drink%20took%20over.%20The%20kind%20who%20might%20not%20be%20around%20to%20see%20his%20child%20grow%20up%20if%20he%20kept%20going%20down%20this%20road.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20morning%20after%20the%20crash%2C%20I%20admitted%20to%20myself%20that%20I%20couldn't%20keep%20living%20like%20this.%20I%20embarked%2C%20once%20again%2C%20on%20my%20recovery%20journey.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20my%20intent%20was%20absolute.%20I'm%20seven%20months%20sober.%20But%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsobriety-stopped-drinking-secretly-alcohol-identity-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esobriety%20is%20just%20one%20part%20of%20my%20journey%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20more%20emotional%20work%20has%20been%20rebuilding%20my%20relationship%20with%20my%20son%20and%20earning%20back%20the%20trust%20that%20I%20broke.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChildren%20%E2%80%94%20even%20at%20the%20tender%20age%20of%204%2C%20as%20my%20son%20is%20%E2%80%94%20have%20a%20better%20sense%20of%20the%20world%20around%20them%20than%20we%20understand.%20My%20son%20might%20not%20have%20known%20I%20was%20drinking%2C%20but%20I%20know%20he%20felt%20the%20distance.%20He%20noticed%20when%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychology-how-much-people-watch-each-other-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewasn't%20paying%20attention%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20him%20and%20when%20I%20overreacted%20to%20small%20things%20because%20I%20was%20nursing%20a%20hangover.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22535ad085-71ba-4cc9-a199-5a8c50fc94fc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can't%20forgive%20myself%20for%20what%20I%20did%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-let-go-of-secrets-causing-you-shame2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshame%20and%20guilt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20knowing%20how%20my%20choices%20shaped%20Neil's%20early%20years%20is%20something%20I%20carry%20with%20me%20every%20day.%20Those%20first%20few%20years%20of%20his%20life%20should%20have%20been%20about%20joy%2C%20security%2C%20and%20connection.%20Instead%2C%20my%20addiction%20robbed%20us%20of%20moments%20we'll%20never%20get%20back.%20And%20as%20hard%20I%20try%2C%20and%20as%20much%20as%20I%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20doing%20so%2C%20I'll%20never%20forgive%20myself%20for%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%2C%20in%20recovery%2C%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20make%20up%20for%20lost%20time.%20I%20intended%20to%20dive%20into%20parenting%20with%20everything%20I%20had.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20the%20dad%20who%20shows%20up%20when%20he%20says%20he%20will%2C%20takes%20his%20son%20to%20the%20park%2C%20and%20never%20misses%20bedtime.%20And%20I%20have%20been%20doing%20those%20things.%20But%2C%20as%20I%20failed%20to%20realize%2C%20trust%20takes%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20parts%20of%20recovery%2C%20undoubtedly%2C%20has%20been%20accepting%20that%20my%20son%20needs%20time%20to%20trust%20me%20again.%20When%20I%20pick%20him%20up%20from%20nursery%2C%20I%20see%20%E2%80%94%20now%20and%20then%20%E2%80%94%20the%20hesitation%20in%20his%20eyes%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20doubt%20I%20put%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b932aaf-f4de-40b4-986c-6e7a39339bac%5C%22%3EI'm%20focused%20on%20rebuilding%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20first%2C%20that%20reaction%20devastated%20me.%20But%2C%20over%20time%2C%20I've%20learned%20to%20see%20it%20as%20part%20of%20the%20process.%20Rebuilding%20trust%20isn't%20about%20grand%20gestures%3B%20it's%20about%20showing%20up%20consistently%2C%20day%20after%20day.%20It's%20about%20reading%20the%20bedtime%20story%20even%20when%20I'm%20tired%20or%20sitting%20on%20the%20floor%20to%20build%20a%20Lego%20tower%20when%20my%20mind%20is%20racing%20with%20recovery%20challenges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20also%20%E2%80%94%20as%20part%20of%20my%20recovery%20%E2%80%94%20been%20having%20difficult%20conversations%20with%20Neil.%20At%204%2C%20my%20son%20is%20too%20young%20to%20comprehend%20addiction%2C%20but%20I've%20started%20explaining%20it%20in%20simple%20terms.%20I%20tell%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BDaddy%20used%20to%20make%20bad%20choices%2C%20but%20now%20I'm%20working%20hard%20to%20make%20better%20ones.%26quot%3B%20I%20want%20him%20to%20see%20that%20it's%20OK%20to%20admit%20when%20you've%20messed%20up%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20you're%20willing%20to%20do%20the%20work%20to%20make%20things%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParenting%20while%20in%20recovery%20is%20a%20balancing%20act.%20It's%20about%20managing%20my%20healing%20while%20staying%20present%20for%20my%20son.%20It's%20about%20showing%20him%2C%20through%20my%20actions%2C%20that%20people%20can%20change%20and%20that%20mistakes%20don't%20have%20to%20define%20you.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20his%20life%20%E2%80%94%20and%20mine%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20showing%20up%20as%20my%20true%20self.%20And%20for%20me%2C%20that's%20the%20greatest%20victory%20of%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-sober-for-my-child-need-to-regain-his-trust-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735561442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674667d89f2901eb60373237%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-sober-for-my-child-need-to-regain-his-trust-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20wake%20up%20call%20with%20alcohol%20came%20after%20I%20crashed%20my%20care%20while%20driving%20under%20the%20influence.%20I%20broke%20so%20many%20promises%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20that%20dad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alister%20Ross)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-sober-for-my-child-need-to-regain-his-trust-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20'f**k%20in%20the%20face'%20to%20'please%20post...'%3A%20What%20happened%20to%20Elon%20Musk%20in%2048%20hours%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735561151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116800748%2Cimgsize-7