D%5C%223917%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20went%20with%20his%20wife%20to%20Disney%20World%20without%20their%20kids.%3Cp%3EGary%20Hershorn%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20had%20enough%20airline%20miles%20for%20two%20round-trip%20first-class%20tickets%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20Orlando.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20enjoyed%20the%20experiences%20and%20our%20time%20together%20and%20reconnected%20as%20a%20couple.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20would%20be%20no%20penny-pinching%20on%20this%20trip%2C%20unlike%20our%20first%20as%20parents.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20from%20Southern%20California%2C%20many%20would%20ask%20why%20I'd%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20money%20to%20go%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-tourists-should-never-do-disney-parks-former-employee-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWalt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Florida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20when%20I%20had%20Disneyland%20in%20my%20backyard.%20I%20would%20say%20that%20if%20you%20ask%20that%20question%2C%20you've%20never%20been%20there.%20It%20is%20a%20magical%20world%20unto%20itself.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20first%20trip%20was%20in%201987%2C%20and%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20made%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-free-travel-agent-plan-disney-trip-big-group-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannual%20trips%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20until%201993%20when%20we%20found%20out%20we%20were%20going%20to%20be%20parents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnyone%20with%20kids%20knows%20that%20life%20changes.%20We%20waited%20until%20our%20son%20was%20old%20enough%20and%20returned%20as%20a%20family%20in%201998.%20It%20was%20even%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-my-3-kids-to-disney-world-best-worst-parts-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emore%20magical%20with%20children%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20By%20the%20time%20he%20was%208%2C%20we%20gave%20him%20a%20walkie-talkie%20and%20let%20him%20run%20around%20the%20hotel%20as%20long%20as%20he%20checked%20in%20with%20us.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20that%20one%20day%2C%20we%20would%20return%20without%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a9abd87-f0ef-459f-846a-8253890bd21c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20when%20he%20was%20a%20teenager%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELife%20is%20all%20about%20change%2C%20especially%20with%20kids.%20The%20next%20two%20decades%20saw%20many%20family%20trips%20to%20the%20magical%20world%20in%20Florida.%20When%20the%20economy%20changed%20in%202007%2C%20we%20switched%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-family-vacations-better-than-luxury-travel-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edriving%20across%20the%20Western%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20our%20camping%20trailer%2C%20but%20always%20as%20a%20family.%20Being%20a%20dad%20wasn't%20just%20something%20I%20did%3B%20it%20was%20who%20I%20was.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20life%20changes%3B%20children%20don't%20stay%20children%20forever.%20As%20a%20teen%2C%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20cool%20for%20my%20son%20to%20go%20on%20trips%20with%20Mom%20and%20Dad.%20Then%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frenovated-backyard-for-sons-wedding-investment-paid-off-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20inevitable%20happened%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20high%20school%20graduation%2C%20college%2C%20and%20the%20Army.%20We%20had%20officially%20become%20empty-nesters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%202017%2C%20our%20financial%20situation%20had%20improved%2C%20and%20I%20was%20once%20again%20working%20as%20an%20executive.%20I%20felt%20secure%20and%20decided%20it%20was%20time%20to%20reward%20ourselves.%20It%20would%20be%20our%20first%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandpa-spent-6000-disney-trip-with-family-mistakes-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etrip%20to%20Disney%20World%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20without%20kids%20in%20decades%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20weird.%20We%20had%20originally%20planned%20for%20September%2C%20but%20Hurricane%20Irma%20had%20other%20plans.%20We%20rescheduled%20for%20February%20of%202018.%20We'd%20never%20gone%20in%20Spring%3B%20we'd%20always%20gone%20in%20August%20to%20close%20out%20the%20summer%20before%20school%20started.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5a04eab-c385-4758-b488-ecdbb33491d5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20hit%20all%20the%20parks%20when%20we%20went%20by%20ourselves%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20worked%20late%20the%20night%20before%20answering%20final%20emails.%20Then%20I%20clicked%20%26quot%3Bsave%26quot%3B%20on%20my%20out-of-office%20message.%20I%20was%20officially%20on%20vacation.%20I%20had%20years%20of%20airline%20miles%20accumulated%20and%20had%20enough%20for%20two%20first-class%20round-trip%20tickets.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20headed%20first%20to%20Universal%20Studios%20and%20a%20two-night%20stay%20at%20the%20Royal%20Pacific%20Resort%20Hotel.%20We%20did%20all%20the%20parks%20and%20all%20the%20Harry%20Potter%20attractions.%20We%20even%20got%20a%20Butter%20Beer.%20But%20we'd%20come%20to%20Florida%20for%20another%20reason.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20our%20third%20day%2C%20we%20drove%20to%20Disney's%20Wilderness%20Lodge.%20We've%20stayed%20at%20a%20half%20dozen%20resorts%20on%20the%20property%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20this%20is%20our%20favorite.%20The%20architecture%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20great%20national%20park%20lodges.%20A%20pine%20forest%20surrounds%20it%20and%20overlooks%20Bay%20Lake.%20There%20is%20even%20a%20geyser%20(artificial)%20that%20erupts%20regularly.%20Our%20room%20overlooked%20the%20lake%2C%20pool%2C%20and%20geyser.%20Every%20nigh%2Ct%20we%20watched%20the%20Bay%20Lake%20Electrical%20Water%20Pageant%20from%20our%20balcony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b01d4a8b-86c8-4039-b60e-8e80a437cab8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trip%20brought%20back%20so%20many%20memories%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20at%20Disney%20World%20just%20as%20a%20couple%20brought%20back%20a%20lot%20of%20memories.%20We%20were%20a%20little%20older%2C%20but%20it%20was%20as%20if%20no%20time%20had%20passed%20at%20all%20since%20that%20first%20trip%20as%20a%20young%20couple%20all%20those%20years%20ago%2C%20except%20that%20I%20had%20less%20hair.%20One%20of%20my%20favorite%20photos%20of%20all%20time%20is%20from%20this%20trip.%20It's%20a%20selfie%20of%20us%20at%20the%20Universal%20Hotel%2C%20me%20in%20my%20Disney%20polo%20shirt%2C%20her%20auburn%20hair%20gently%20resting%20on%20her%20bare%20shoulders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHolding%20hands%2C%20we%20walked%20to%20the%20Magic%20Kingdom.%20For%20the%20next%20six%20days%2C%20we%20hopped%20from%20one%20park%20to%20the%20next.%20Exploring%20all%20the%20changes%20to%20the%20resort%20since%20our%20last%20trip.%20Enjoying%20all%20the%20rides%2C%20shows%2C%20attractions%2C%20and%20dining%20experiences.%20EPCOT%20was%20having%20its%20International%20Flower%20%26amp%3B%20Garden%20Festival.%20The%20park%20was%20filled%20with%20beautiful%20floral%20displays%20and%20unique%20food%20carts%20in%20every%20land.%20We%20rented%20bikes%20at%20the%20Fort%20Wilderness%20Campground%20and%20had%20a%20picnic%20lunch%20by%20the%20lake.%20Walked%20around%20Disney%20Springs%20and%20toured%20the%20hotels%20and%20the%20campground.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20perfect%20trip%2C%20but%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20I%20would%20do%20differently%20next%20time%20is%20not%20have%20a%20rental%20car.%20Though%20the%20Alamo%20rental%20was%20only%20%24331%20for%20the%20eight%20days%2C%20it%20was%20another%20%2425%20per%20day%20for%20parking%20at%20the%20hotel.%20And%20the%20traffic%20was%20so%20bad%20on%20the%20resort%20that%20we%20ended%20up%20just%20using%20the%20resort%20transit.%20The%20hotel%20cost%20for%208%20days%20was%20%243%2C697.%20We%20also%20spent%20another%20%242%2C080%20on%20taxes%2C%20dining%2C%20and%20souvenirs%20on%20our%20Disney%20gift%20card%20from%20our%20Chase%20Disney%20Rewards%20Visa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20I%20did%20have%20to%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20work%20calls%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Ballowed%26quot%3B%20one%20hour%20per%20day%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20emails%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20vacations%20in%20a%20long%20time%20where%20I%20felt%20relaxed%20and%20refreshed.%20We%20didn't%20have%20an%20itinerary%2C%20no%20schedule%20to%20keep.%20We%20enjoyed%20the%20experiences%20and%20our%20time%20together%20and%20reconnected%20as%20a%20couple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Four-first-trip-to-disney-world-without-kids-reconnected-couple-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735561141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67466b3afa0140cdd565bf79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Four-first-trip-to-disney-world-without-kids-reconnected-couple-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20wife%20and%20I%20enjoyed%20our%20time%20together%20and%20reconnected%20during%20a%20trip%20to%20Disney%20World%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20There%20was%20no%20penny-pinching%20and%20we%20had%20a%20blast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chris%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A130%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Four-first-trip-to-disn