C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20stepped%20inside%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESurprisingly%20enough%2C%20the%20hostel%20had%20its%20own%20brand%20of%20luxury.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20images.%20Left%3A%20A%20white%20bunk%20bed%20with%20a%20ladder%20on%20the%20left%20leading%20to%20the%20top%20bunk%20and%20gray%20curtains%20over%20each%20bed.%20Right%3A%20The%20author%20sits%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20the%20curtain%20closed%20behind%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6711423001ea6d83dee1e4f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter's%20bunk%20at%20Cache%20House%2C%20an%20upscale%20hostel.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hostel%20was%20located%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Anvil%20Hotel.%20Inside%2C%20it%20was%20clean%20and%20modern%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20Western%20flair.%20There%20was%20a%20spacious%20communal%20space%2C%20a%20large%20bathroom%20with%20private%20shower%20and%20toilet%20stalls%2C%20high-end%20toiletries%2C%20and%20locked%20storage%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20intentionally%20booked%20my%20low-budget%20stay%20on%20the%20final%20night%20because%20I%20thought%20I%20might%20not%20sleep%20as%20well%20and%20would%20be%20able%20to%20nap%20on%20the%20plane%20ride%20home.%20But%20thanks%20to%20a%20night%20of%20deep%20sleep%2C%20I%20was%20awake%20the%20whole%20way%20back%20to%20NYC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20bed%20in%20my%20top%20bunk%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20get%20up.%20Like%20my%20other%20two%20stays%2C%20the%20mattress%20was%20firm%20with%20just%20enough%20give.%20And%20wool%20bedding%20made%20it%20just%20as%20cozy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20credit%20my%20good%20night's%20rest%20to%20the%20unexpected%20level%20of%20privacy.%20My%20bunk%20felt%20like%20a%20secluded%20nook%20with%20light%20