%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20certainly%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20proposals%2C%26quot%3B%20Lavrov%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIdea%20floating%20included%20posting%20European%20troops%20in%20a%20buffer%20zone%2C%20and%20distancing%20Ukraine%20from%20NATO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergey%20Lavrov%20rejected%20plans%20associated%20with%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Russian%20state%20news%20agency%20TASS%20published%20Monday%2C%20Lavrov%20criticized%20what%20he%20said%20he%20understood%20Trump's%20plane%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20how%20he%20phrased%20it%2C%20per%20an%20English%20translation%20of%20the%20interview%20posted%20by%20Russian's%20foreign%20ministry%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3B%E2%80%A6their%20idea%20is%20to%20suspend%20hostilities%20along%20the%20line%20of%20contact%20and%20transfer%20responsibility%20for%20confrontation%20with%20Russia%20to%20the%20Europeans.%20We%20are%20not%20happy%2C%20of%20course%2C%20with%20the%20proposals%20made%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Trump%20team%20to%20postpone%20Ukraine's%20admission%20to%20NATO%20for%2020%20years%20and%20to%20station%20British%20and%20European%20peacekeeping%20forces%20in%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plans%20have%20not%20officially%20been%20announced%20by%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20they%20resemble%20a%20report%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Ftrump-presidency-ukraine-russia-war-plans-008655c0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20unnamed%20people%20close%20to%20the%20president-elect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20claimed%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20that%20he%20could%20bring%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20to%20an%20end%20within%20days%2C%20but%20said%20he%20would%20not%20describe%20how.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3