2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20have%20arrested%20a%20man%20who%20hired%20Thanakarn%20Kanthee%20aka%20%26quot%3BBank%20Leicester%26quot%3B%20to%20take%20on%20the%20deadly%20challenge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthai-influencer-dies-after-guzzling-whisky-bottles-in-deadly-rs-75-000-challenge-7363542%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20A%20Murky%20Rivalry%20Is%20Brewing%20In%20India's%20Neighbourhood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flpiidog8_taliban-checks-books_625x300_20_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghans%20are%20understandably%20furious.%20After%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20of%20unleashing%20terror%20on%20them%20from%20the%20mujahideen%20era%20through%20the%20Taliban%20times%2C%20Pakistan%20decided%20to%20bomb%20Afghan%20villages%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20killing%20some%2046%20people%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children.%20The%20villages%20allegedly%20sheltered%20the%20cadres%20of%20the%20Tehrik-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20ironic.%20The%20TTP%20is%20hardly%20an%20Afghan%20product.%20It%20is%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20the%20final%20result%20of%20Pakistan's%20own%20disastrous%20policy%20of%20backing%20and%20sheltering%20a%20variety%20of%20terrorists.%20Remember%20Hillary%20Clinton's%20famous%20jibe%20in%202011%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20Pakistan%20keeping%20snakes%20in%20its%20backyard%20that%20would%20inevitably%20turn%20around%20and%20strike%20its%20benefactor%3F%20This%20seems%20to%20be%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20The%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20diplomacy%20seems%20a%20little%20quixotic%2C%20though%20one%20can%20never%20tell%20with%20regard%20to%20Islamabad.%20Veteran%20diplomat%20Mohammad%20Sadiq%2C%20who%20has%20served%20six%20years%20as%20an%20ambassador%20and%20is%20now%20a%20reappointed%20special%20representative%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20was%20in%20Kabul%20recently.%20By%20his%20own%20account%2C%20he%20received%20a%20gracious%20welcome%2C%20especially%20by%20the%20Foreign%20Ministry%20led%20by%20Amir%20Khan%20Muttaqi.%20The%20latter%20has%20been%20a%20frequent%20guest%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20both%20in%20the%20past%20and%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20was%20once%20seen%20strolling%20with%20Foreign%20Minister%20Bilawal.%20According%20to%20a%20formal%20statement%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Emirate%20of%20Afghanistan%20declared%20its%20determination%20to%20maintain%20good%20relations%20and%20encourage%20trade%20and%20transit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20very%20encouraging.%20Hours%20later%20though%2C%20Pakistani%20fighter%20aircraft%20were%20bombing%20and%20strafing%20Barmal%20in%20Paktika%2C%20a%20province%20that%20is%20the%20hometown%20of%20Muttaqi.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20some%2046%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20Barmal%3B%20the%20strikes%20also%20apparently%20hit%20a%20refugee%20camp.%20Pakistan%20claimed%20that%20it%20had%20targeted%20TTP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Akhtar%20Muhammad%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20TTP's%20Umar%20Media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20apparently%20furious%20Kabul%20summoned%20the%20Pakistani%20charge%20d'affairs%20and%20issued%20a%20strong%20protest%2C%20calling%20the%20strikes%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20attempt%20by%20certain%20circles%20in%20Pakistan%20aimed%20at%20undermining%20trust%20and%20causing%20friction%20in%20the%20relations%20of%20the%20two%20nations%E2%80%9D%20(meaning%2C%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20army)%20and%20declaring%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Pakistani%20side%20has%20been%20clearly%20informed%20that%20protecting%20Afghanistan's%20national%20sovereignty%20is%20a%20red%20line%20for%20the%20Islamic%20Emirate%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20such%20actions%20are%20viewed%20highly%20irresponsible%20and%20will%20inevitably%20bear%20repercussions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20a%20statement.%20Afghanistan%20doesn't%20have%20an%20army%20in%20the%20conventional%20sense%2C%20but%20a%20threat%20from%20a%20country%20that%20has%20exhausted%20empires%20and%20superpowers%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20seriously.%20True%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20government%20has%20a%20%E2%80%98Made%20in%20Pakistan'%20stamp%2C%20but%20Afghans%20have%20rarely%20ever%20taken%20attacks%20lying%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Homemade%20Threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20attacks%20are%20clear%20in%20one%20respect.%20The%20Pakistanis%20have%20endured%20a%20lot.%20According%20to%20available%20data%2C%20Pakistan%20faced%20as%20many%20as%20785%20attacks%20in%20just%20this%20year%2C%20with%2055%20security%20forces%20lost%20in%20the%20first%20weeks%20of%20November%20alone.%20Just%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20a%20most%20brutal%20attack%20in%20Makeen%20reportedly%20killed%2035%20soldiers.%20This%20was%20probably%20the%20immediate%20trigger%20for%20the%20air%20attacks%20even%20as%20Pakistani%20security%20forces%20launched%20a%20so-called%20'IBO'%20(Intelligence%20based%20operation)%20in%20the%20areas%20opposite%20Paktia%20to%20flush%20out%20terrorists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20such%20operations%20have%20led%20to%20a%20more%20deleterious%20effect%20than%20success.%20Earlier%2C%20policemen%20would%20rebel%20against%20Pakistan%20army%20operations%20in%20Lakki%20Marwat%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20military%20quit%20%E2%80%98meddling'%20in%20the%20area%2C%20even%20as%20hundreds%20blocked%20the%20Indus%20Highway%20in%20protest.%20Further%20north%20is%20the%20unending%20conflict%20in%20Kurram%2C%20where%20a%20Shia%20majority%20is%20battling%20the%20state's%20attempts%20to%20settle%20in%20more%20Sunnis.%20Kurram%2C%20being%20the%20shortest%20route%20to%20reach%20Kabul%2C%20has%20long%20been%20a%20major%20ingress%20point%20for%20operations%20into%20Afghanistan.%20That%20such%20operations%20continue%20is%20a%20given.%20The%20locals%20are%20tired%20of%20being%20pawns%20in%20a%20game%20played%20by%20Rawalpindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPashtuns%20Are%20Unhappy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20to%20all%20this%20unhappiness%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20after%20the%20arrests%20of%20leaders%20of%20the%20peaceful%20Pashtun%20Tahaffuz%20Movement%20(Pashtun%20Protection%20Force%2C%20or%20PTM)%2C%20including%20the%20charismatic%20Manzur%20Pashteen.%20After%20half%20a%20century%20of%20exploitation%20and%20violence%2C%20all%20they%20were%20asking%20for%20was%20peace%2C%20removal%20of%20all%20mines%2C%20an%20end%20to%20humiliating%20check%20posts%2C%20and%20free%20movement%20into%20Afghanistan.%20In%20December%2C%20Islamabad%20also%20chose%20to%20ban%20the%20PTM%20and%20followed%20that%20up%20with%20arresting%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20movement.%20That%20is%20hardly%20likely%20to%20improve%20matters%20given%20that%20Pashtuns%2C%20the%20second-largest%20ethnic%20group%20in%20the%20country%2C%20will%20only%20end%20up%20feeling%20even%20more%20alienated%20and%20might%20be%20pushed%20further%20towards%20jihadi%20groups.%20In%20short%2C%20with%20the%20whole%20border%20on%20fire%2C%20any%20group%20will%20face%20is%20unlikely%20to%20face%20difficulty%20in%20getting%20recruits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeclarations%20Of%20Retribution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKabul%20has%20promised%20retribution.%20Attacks%20on%20security%20personnel%20have%20gone%20up%20hugely.%20Kabul%20can%20upscale%20these%20and%20perhaps%20even%20take%20on%20a%20larger%20target.%20But%20here's%20the%20thing%3A%20the%20Taliban%20are%20heavily%20divided%2C%20with%20leaders%20like%20Sirajuddin%20Haqqani%20and%20Muttaqi%2C%20among%20others%2C%20being%20more%20Pakistani%20than%20Afghan.%20The%20assassination%20of%20Siraj's%20powerful%20uncle%20Khalil%20Haqqani%2C%20claimed%20by%20the%20IS-K%2C%20could%20not%20have%20happened%20without%20some%20insider%20support.%20Khalil%20was%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20Kandahar%20leadership%2C%20which%2C%20apart%20from%20being%20heavily%20conservative%2C%20has%20a%20faction%20of%20clerics%20who%20have%20studied%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20are%20affiliated%20with%20major%20madrassas%20there.%20Add%20to%20this%20the%20fact%20that%20Haqqani%20and%20others%20have%20their%20support%20bases%20in%20areas%20bombed%20both%20recently%20as%20well%20as%20earlier%20in%20March.%20In%20sum%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20airstrikes%20were%20a%20warning%20by%20Rawalpindi%20to%20get%20greater%20control%20of%20decision-making%20in%20Kabul%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20push%20for%20action%20against%20those%20TTP%20factions%20that%20are%20attacking%20Pakistan.%20Rawalpindi%2C%20as%20is%20its%20practice%2C%20has%20its%20own%20factions%20that%20it%20can%20use%20for%20its%20%E2%80%98strategic'%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Taliban%20are%20in%20a%20cleft%20stick.%20Action%20against%20the%20TTP%20may%20just%20lead%20to%20more%20recruits%20for%20the%20Islamic%20State%20in%20Khorasan%20(IS-K)%2C%20Kabul's%20biggest%20threat.%20For%20the%20Taliban%2C%20support%20from%20China%20and%20Russia%20depends%20heavily%20on%20its%20actions%20against%20IS-K%2C%20something%20UN%20reports%20acknowledge.%20UN%20reports%20also%20observe%20that%20the%20IS-K%20is%20strengthening%20with%20about%206%2C000%20fighters.%20More%20worryingly%2C%20they%20note%20cooperation%20between%20it%2C%20the%20TTP%20and%20al%20Qaeda%2C%20which%20could%20transform%20the%20TTP%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98regional%20threat'%20against%20India%2C%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh.%20That's%20a%20new%20development%2C%20though%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20support%20that%20the%20TTP%20or%20its%20affiliates%20have%20any%20interest%20in%20India.%20The%20IS-K%2C%20however%2C%20has%20released%20a%20barrage%20of%20propaganda%20material%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3ESawt%20al%20Hind%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Voice%20of%20Hind)%20and%20other%20publications%2C%20to%20highlight%20Hindu-Muslim%20divisions%20in%20India.%20Delhi%20will%20be%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20such%20developments%20keeping%20in%20mind%20Pakistan's%20continued%20ability%20to%20influence%20multiple%20factions%20in%20Afghanistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20needs%20to%20engage%20more%20strongly%20with%20Kabul%20and%20Kandahar%20and%20watch%20closely%20the%20multiple%20players%20now%20active%20along%20the%20Pakistan-Afghanistan%20border%2C%20including%20a%20new%20al%20Qaeda%20presence%20in%20Nangarhar.%20There%20is%20a%20puzzling%20mix%20of%20motives%20here%2C%20including%20individual%20ambitions%20of%20Taliban%20leaders%2C%20Pashtun%20nationalism%2C%20and%2C%20most%20significant%20of%20all%2C%20the%20continuing%20Pakistani%20determination%20to%20dominate%20Afghanistan.%20That%20has%20never%20died%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20likely%20to%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20This%20is%20the%20one%20constant%20for%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20prism%20through%20which%20all%20actions%20by%20Pakistan%20need%20to%20be%20viewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20wait%20for%20it.%20A%20huge%20backlash%20can%20be%20expected%20as%20local%20Taliban%20leaders%20react%20in%20anger%2C%20and%20if%20this%20is%20encouraged%20by%20Kabul%2C%20a%20large%20incursion%20into%20the%20tribal%20areas%20can't%20be%20ruled%20out.%20Never%20has%20the%20Durand%20Line%20been%20more%20dangerous%2C%20but%20the%20real%20threat%20would%20emerge%20if%20the%20anger%20along%20the%20border%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20coalesces%20into%20one%20mighty%20backlash.%20Watch%20that%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Tara%20Kartha%20is%20a%20former%20Director%20in%20the%20NSCS)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735558740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flpiidog8_taliban-checks-books_625x300_20_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-murky-pakistan-afghanistan-rivalry-is-brewing-in-indias-neighbourhood-7361998%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remember%20Hillary%20Clinton's%20famous%20jibe%20in%202011%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20Pakistan%20keeping%20snakes%20in%20its%20backyard%20that%20would%20inevitably%20turn%20around%20and%20strike%20its%20benefactor%3F%20This%20seems%20to%20be%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-murky-pakistan-afghanistan-rivalry-is-brewing-in-indias-neighbourhood-7361998%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MrBeast%20is%20teasing%20another%20recreation%20of%20'Squid%20Game'%20as%20he%20continues%20to%20furiously%20promote%20'Beast%20Games'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223497%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jimmy%20Donaldson%20AKA%20MrBeast%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67726ff9e7fd9417ec07f6a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222623%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMrBeast%20likes%20to%20stay%20ahead%20and%20is%20already%20teasing%20another%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%26quot%3B%20recreation.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kopaloff%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Prime%20Video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMrBeast%20appears%20to%20be%20plotting%20to%20recreate%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%26quot%3B%20season%202.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20%243.5%20million%20version%20of%20season%201%20is%20likely%20partly%20why%20Amazon%20greenlighted%20%26quot%3BBeast%20Games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20the%20project%20has%20been%20marred%20with%20controversy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-youtube-jimmy-donaldson-net-