a-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladeshi-americans-urge-donald-trump-to-secure-chinmoy-krishna-dass-release-protect-minorities%2Famp_articleshow%2F116795634.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladeshi-americans-urge-donald-trump-to-secure-chinmoy-krishna-dass-release-protect-minorities%2Famp_articleshow%2F116795634.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWould%20Have%20Been%20Better%20If...%26quot%3B%3A%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Take%20On%20Allu%20Arjun's%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERefusing%20to%20blame%20Telangana%20Police%20for%20the%20action%20against%20actor%20Allu%20Arjun%20in%20the%20theatre%20stampede%20case%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20said%20the%20law%20is%20equal%20for%20all%20and%20police%20must%20act%20with%20public%20safety%20in%20mind.%20Mr%20Kalyan%2C%20leader%20of%20NDA%20ally%20Janasena%20Party%2C%20praised%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20A%20Revanth%20Reddy%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20leader%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20that%20Allu%20Arjun%20should%20have%20visited%20the%20family%20of%20the%20woman%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20an%20informal%20interaction%20at%20Mangalagiri%2C%20Mr%20Kalyan%20shared%20his%20perspective%20on%20the%20stampede%20incident%20at%20Hyderabad's%20Sandhya%20Theatre%20on%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllu%20Arjun%20visited%20the%20theatre%20where%20his%20movie%20Pushpa%202%20was%20being%20screened.%20The%20film%20star's%20visit%20led%20to%20chaos.%20A%2035-year-old%20woman%2C%20Revathi%2C%20died%20in%20the%20incident%20and%20her%20son%20was%20injured.%20Soon%20after%2C%20Hyderabad%20police%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20Allu%20Arjun.%20He%20was%20arrested%20and%20granted%20bail%20shortly%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kalyan%20today%20said%20it%20was%20important%20for%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20to%20prioritise%20public%20safety.%20%26quot%3BThe%20law%20is%20equal%20for%20all%2C%20and%20I%20do%20not%20blame%20the%20police%20in%20such%20incidents%2C%20they%20act%20with%20public%20safety%20in%20mind.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20theater%20staff%20should%20have%20informed%20Allu%20Arjun%20earlier%20about%20any%20issues.%20Once%20he%20sat%20in%20the%20seat%2C%20they%20should%20have%20instructed%20him%20to%20vacate%20it%20if%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kalyan%20is%20related%20to%20Allu%20Arjun.%20Allu%20Arjun's%20aunt%20Surekha%20is%20married%20to%20renowned%20actor%20Chiranjeevi%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20elder%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20have%20been%20better%20if%20someone%20had%20visited%20the%20victim's%20family%20earlier%20on%20behalf%20of%20Allu%20Arjun.%20Revathi's%20death%20in%20this%20incident%20has%20deeply%20shocked%20me.%20They%20turned%20what%20was%20already%20lost%20into%20an%20even%20greater%20tragedy.%20We%20should%20have%20conveyed%20earlier%20that%20we%20are%20all%20here%20to%20support%20the%20family.%20There%20should%20have%20been%20a%20sense%20of%20regret%20for%20the%20mistake%2C%20even%20if%20it%20happened%20without%20their%20direct%20involvement.%C2%A0There%20is%20a%20clear%20lack%20of%20humanity%20in%20this%20matter.%20Everyone%20should%20have%20gone%20to%20Revathi's%20house%20to%20offer%20reassurance%20and%20condolences.%20The%20people's%20anger%20stems%20from%20the%20absence%20of%20such%20a%20gesture.%20Arjun%2C%20too%2C%20feels%20the%20pain%20of%20knowing%20that%20someone%20lost%20their%20life%20because%20of%20this%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Kalyan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECinema%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20a%20collaborative%20effort.%20%3AIt%20is%20not%20fair%20to%20make%20Allu%20Arjun%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20incident.%20Telangana%20CM%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20responded%20appropriately%20to%20the%20developments%20following%20the%20stampede.%20Sometimes%2C%20decisions%20are%20dictated%20by%20circumstances.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20even%20Chiranjeevi%20used%20to%20watch%20movies%20with%20his%20fans.%20Otherwise%2C%20he%20would%20wear%20a%20mask%20and%20go%20to%20the%20theater%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Andhra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20described%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Reddy%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20has%20risen%20from%20humble%20beginnings.%20%26quot%3BTelangana%20CM%20Revanth%20Reddy%20is%20a%20great%20leader%2C%20who%20has%20risen%20from%20humble%20beginnings.%20He%20did%20not%20do%20like%20YSRCP%2C%20but%20instead%20focused%20on%20providing%20benefits%20in%20his%20state.%20Flexibility%20was%20granted%20for%20increasing%20ticket%20prices%2C%20which%20boosted%20movie%20collections.%20Films%20like%20Salaar%20and%20Pushpa%202%20achieved%20massive%20box%20office%20success%20with%20his%20cooperation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sandhya%20Theatre%20incident%20has%20divided%20public%20opinion%2C%20with%20many%20questioning%20how%20Allu%20Arjun%20could%20be%20blamed%20for%20the%20stampede%20death%20and%20another%20section%20arguing%20that%20he%20cannot%20escape%20accountability%20just%20because%20he%20is%20a%20film%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20face-off%2C%20a%20delegation%20from%20the%20Telugu%20film%20industry%20met%20Chief%20Minister%20Reddy.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20told%20the%20delegation%20that%20the%20industry%20has%20full%20support%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20but%20there%20will%20be%20no%20compromise%20on%20law%20and%20order.%C2%A0%26quot%3BAs%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20it%20is%20my%20responsibility%20to%20enforce%20the%20law.%20I%20do%20not%20have%20any%20personal%20preferences%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20quoted%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735551900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnad4ifhg_pawan-kalyan-al