ise%20her%20to%20come%20forward%20with%20any%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20Alison%20Lawrie%20from%20Corstorphine%20Police%20Station%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20at%20the%20time%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20now%20know%20that%20Santra%20picked%20up%20a%20black%20and%20white%20shopper%20style%20bag%20from%20an%20address%20in%20Burnvale%20on%20Friday%20evening%2C%20but%20she%20did%20not%20have%20it%20when%20she%20entered%20the%20supermarket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bag%20is%20distinctive%20and%20someone%20may%20remember%20seeing%20her%20carrying%20it.%20We%20are%20continuing%20to%20review%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20have%20released%20images%20of%20Santra%20from%20the%20supermarket%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20someone%20recognises%20her.%20Extensive%20enquiries%20are%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20trace%20her.%E2%80%9D%20Her%20friends%20and%20family%20had%20said%20the%20disappearance%20was%20out%20of%20character%20and%20had%20become%20very%20worried%20for%20her%20safety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735550040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fup82mi6g_santra-saju_625x300_30_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fsantra-saju-body-of-missing-22-year-old-indian-student-found-in-scotland-river-7362276%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20body%20of%20a%2022-year-old%20Indian%20student%20missing%20since%20earlier%20this%20month%20has%20been%20found%20in%20a%20river%20in%20Scotland%20and%20her%20family%20has%20been%20informed%20while%20formal%20identification%20is%20awaited.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fsantra-saju-body-of-missing-22-year-old-indian-student-found-in-scotland-river-7362276%2