nama%20relations%20and%20significantly%20impacted%20the%20geopolitical%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Panama%20Canal%20Treaty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJimmy%20Carter%2C%20in%201977%2C%C2%A0signed%20treaties%20with%20Panamanian%20leader%20Gen.%20Omar%20Torrijos%2C%20which%20set%20in%20motion%20the%20gradual%20handover%20of%20the%20canal%20-%20a%20vital%20shipping%20route%20that%20had%20been%20under%20US%20control%20for%20over%2075%20years.%20The%20Panama%20Canal%20Treaty%2C%20agreed%20upon%20by%20both%20leaders%2C%20promised%20Panama%20full%20control%20by%20December%2031%2C%201999%2C%20while%20the%20Treaty%20of%20Permanent%20Neutrality%20ensured%20the%20canal%20would%20remain%20open%20to%20vessels%20of%20all%20nations%2C%20and%20granted%20the%20US%C2%A0the%20right%20to%20defend%20it%20against%20any%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20shift.%20The%20US%20had%20been%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20the%20Canal%20Zone%2C%20a%2082-km%20long%2C%2016-km%20wide%20stretch%20of%20land%20in%20Panama%20that%20was%20essentially%20a%20US%20enclave%2C%20complete%20with%20its%20own%20government%2C%20courts%2C%20and%20military%20presence.%20But%20resentment%20had%20been%20growing%20in%20Panama%2C%20with%20increasing%20calls%20for%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20canal%20and%20an%20end%20to%20the%20segregationist%20policies%20of%20the%20Canal%20Zone%2C%20which%20had%20created%20inequality%20between%20US%20residents%20and%20Panamanians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20saw%20the%20transfer%20of%20control%20as%20a%20surrender%20to%20a%20military%20dictatorship%2C%20while%20others%20viewed%20it%20as%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20ending%20colonial%20legacies.%20The%20treaty%20had%20a%20tough%20battle%20in%20the%20US%20Senate%2C%20but%20with%20support%20from%20unexpected%20sources%2C%20including%20Hollywood%20star%20John%20Wayne%2C%20it%20was%20ratified.%20The%20handover%20process%20began%20in%201977%2C%20with%20Panama%20gradually%20taking%20on%20administrative%20and%20military%20duties.%20By%201999%2C%20Panama%20had%20gained%20the%20expertise%20to%20manage%20the%20canal%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump%20Threatens%20To%20Take%20Over%20Panama%20Canal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20threatened%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-donald-trumps-big-warning-over-panama-canal-amid-rising-chinese-influence-7315582%C2%A0%5C%22%3Ereclaim%20US%20control%20over%20the%20Panama%20Canal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusing%20Panama%20of%20charging%20%26quot%3Bexcessive%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20use.%20The%20President-elect%20also%20warned%20that%20he%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20canal%20to%20fall%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20potential%20Chinese%20influence.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20canal%20was%20%26quot%3Bsolely%20for%20Panama%20to%20manage%2C%20not%20China%20or%20anyone%20else.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20threatened%20that%20if%20Panama%20did%20not%20adhere%20to%20certain%20conditions%2C%20the%20US%20would%20demand%20the%20canal%20be%20returned%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPanama's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPanama's%20President%20Jose%20Raul%20Mulino%20has%20firmly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpanama-president-rules-out-talks-with-donald-trump-over-canal-threat-7339958%5C%22%3Erejected%20any%20discussions%20with%C2%A0Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20regarding%20the%20control%20of%20the%20canal.%20Mr%20Mulino%20also%20dismissed%20claims%20of%20Chinese%20influence%20saying%20that%20the%20canal%20is%20%26quot%3BPanamanian%20and%20belongs%20to%20Panamanians%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20is%20no%20possibility%20of%20opening%20any%20discussions%20on%20this%20matter.%20He%20further%20clarified%20that%20the%20canal's%20tolls%20are%20not%20arbitrarily%20set%20by%20Panama's%20president%20or%20administrator%20but%20through%20a%20long-established%2C%20transparent%20process.%20Mr%20Mulino%20also%20emphatically%20denied%C2%A0Trump's%20allegations%20of%20Chinese%20soldiers%20operating%20the%20canal%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20baseless%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735549260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F6i8u4r6g_jimmy-carter-panama-getty-_625x300_30_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjimmy-carter-and-the-panama-canal-treaty-donald-trumps-threat-countrys-response-7361290%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jimmy%20Carter%2C%20the%20former%20US%20president%20who%20dealt%20with%20crises%20like%20the%20Iran%20hostage%20situation%20and%20brokered%20peace%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20died%20on%20Sunday%20at%20the%20age%20of%20100.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjimmy-carter-and-the-panama-canal-treaty-donald-trumps-threat-countrys-response-7361290%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Beach%20Cleanups%20to%20Zero-Waste%20Weddings%3A%20A%20Couple%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Sustainable%E2%80%99%20Love%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20weddings%20are%20often%20celebrated%20with%20grandeur%2C%20but%20they%20come%20at%20a%20staggering%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20financially%20but%20also%20environmentally.%20According%20to%20industry%20experts%2C%20an%20average%20three-day%20Indian%20wedding%20produces%20about%20800%20kilograms%20of%20wet%20waste%20and%201%2C500%20kilograms%20of%20dry%20waste%2C%20from%20single-use%20decorations%20to%20uneaten%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20environmental%20impact%20of%20these%20celebrations%20is%20undeniable%2C%20prompting%20many%20to%20ask%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20more%20sustainable%20way%20to%20tie%20the%20knot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20Malwade%2C%20a%20chief%20officer%20in%20the%20Merchant%20Navy%2C%20and%20his%20wi