%20including%20exclusion%20from%20jobs%2C%20education%20restrictions%20beyond%20sixth%20grade%2C%20and%20limits%20on%20public%20space%20access.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Ftaliban-orders-ngos-to-fire-female-employees-or-face-closure-in-restrictive-edict%2Farticleshow%2F116792864.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Ftaliban-orders-ngos-to-fire-female-employees-or-face-closure-in-restrictive-edict%2Famp_articleshow%2F116792864.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Ftaliban-orders-ngos-to-fire-female-employees-or-face-closure-in-restrictive-edict%2Famp_articleshow%2F116792864.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMentally%20Disturbing%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20Unfiltered%20Take%20On%20Australia%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20on%20Monday%20said%20the%20184-run%20drubbing%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Australia%20in%20the%20fourth%20Test%20here%20is%20%26quot%3Bmentally%20disturbing%26quot%3B%2C%20conceding%20that%20his%20team%20failed%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20match.%20India%20will%20now%20head%20to%20Sydney%20for%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20trailing%201-2%20in%20the%20five-match%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%20The%20series%20finale%20begins%20on%20January%203.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20mentally%20disturbing%20when%20you%20can't%20do%20what%20you%20have%20come%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%2C%20whose%20own%20poor%20form%20has%20been%20under%20the%20scanner%2C%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20pretty%20disappointing.%20There%20are%20ways%20to%20win%20games%20and%20we%20fell%20short%20in%20finding%20ways%20to%20win%20the%20game%20here.%20We%20wanted%20to%20fight%20till%20the%20end%20and%20unfortunately%2C%20we%20couldn't%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20were%20struggling%20at%2090%20for%20six%20in%20their%20second%20innings%20with%20the%20overall%20lead%20yet%20to%20touch%20200%20on%20Sunday%20but%20managed%20to%20make%20it%20a%20340-run%20target%20for%20the%20visitors.%20Rohit%20admitted%20his%20team%20could%20not%20exploit%20the%20favourable%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20Australia%2090%20for%206.%20We%20know%20things%20can%20get%20tough%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20play%20tough%20cricket%20from%20hard%20situations.%20But%20we%20were%20not%20good%20enough.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20my%20room%20and%20thought%20about%20what%20else%20we%20could%20have%20done%20as%20a%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20threw%20everything%20we%20had%2C%20they%20fought%20hard%2C%20especially%20that%20last-wicket%20partnership%2C%20which%20probably%20cost%20us%20the%20game%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20the%20team%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20go%20at%20the%20target%20despite%20its%20daunting%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20340%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20easy.%20We%20tried%20to%20set%20a%20platform%20and%20keep%20wickets%20in%20hand%20for%20the%20last%20two%20sessions%2C%20but%20they%20bowled%20perfectly%20as%20well.%20We%20wanted%20to%20go%20for%20the%20target%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20set%20the%20platform%20from%20our%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbaikar%20lauded%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Reddy%20for%20making%20a%20fine%20hundred%20during%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20and%20hoped%20the%20youngster%20will%20climb%20the%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20coming%20here%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20these%20conditions%20can%20get%20really%20tough%2C%20but%20he%20showed%20great%20character%2C%20solid%20technique%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20everything%20to%20be%20successful%20at%20this%20level%2C%20I%20hope%20he%20goes%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%2C%20and%20he's%20got%20all%20the%20backing%20from%20the%20team%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20also%20patted%20pacer%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20for%20leading%20the%20Indian%20bowling%20attack%20almost%20singlehandedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20brilliant%2C%20We've%20been%20watching%20him%20for%20so%20many%20years%20now%2C%20coming%20here%20and%20getting%20the%20job%20done.%20He's%20not%20a%20statistical%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20just%20wants%20to%20play%20for%20the%20country%20and%20do%20well%20for%20the%20team%2C%20but%20unfortunately%20he's%20not%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20from%20the%20other%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWanted%20to%20take%20India%20win%20out%20of%20equation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20justified%20the%20move%20to%20not%20declare%20their%20second%20innings%2C%20saying%20he%20wanted%20to%20snuff%20out%20any%20chances%20for%20an%20Indian%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20take%20an%20India%20victory%20out%20of%20the%20equation%20(on%20batting%20on%20and%20not%20declaring).%20We%20had%20plenty%20of%20runs%20to%20play%20with%2C%20and%20as%20many%20helmets%20around%20the%20bat%20as%20we%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20into%20our%20lower-order%20batting%2C%20we%20work%20a%20lot%20on%20how%20best%20to%20bowl%20to%20the%20opposition%20batters%20firstly%2C%20but%20also%20how%20we%20can%20contribute%20with%20the%20bat.%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20said%20the%20MCG%20Test%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20he%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20in%20his%20career%20with%20record%20crowds%20turning%20up%20on%20all%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20an%20amazing%20Test%20match%2C%20