%20crisis.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735545420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0q74685o_south-korea-deadly-crash-_625x300_30_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-korea-plane-crash-where-am-i-what-happened-survivor-of-korea-plane-crash-that-killed-179-7362230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22South%20Korea%20Plane%20Crash%3A%20Two%20flight%20attendants%20were%20the%20lone%20survivors%20of%20the%20plane%20crash%20in%20South%20Korea%20that%20killed%20179%20out%20of%20181%20people%20on%20board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-korea-plane-crash-where-am-i-what-happened-survivor-of-korea-plane-crash-that-killed-179-7362230%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20teen%20sentenced%20over%20Dubai%20'holiday%20romance'%20with%2017-year-old%20girl%20surrenders%20to%20authorities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735544520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F12%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-marcus-fakana-sky-dubai_6773113.png%3F20241211112448%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmarcus-fakana-british-teen-sentenced-over-dubai-holiday-romance-with-17-year-old-girl-surrenders-to-authorities-13281583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20British%20teenager%20sentenced%20to%20one%20year%20in%20prison%20in%20Dubai%20after%20a%20%26quot%3Bholiday%20romance%26quot%3B%20with%20a%2017-year-old%20girl%20has%20surrendered%20himself%20to%20authorities%20to%20begin%20his%20sentence%2C%20according%20to%20a%20campaign%20group.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmarcus-fakana-british-teen-sentenced-over-dubai-holiday-romance-with-17-year-old-girl-surrenders-to-authorities-13281583%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.