ia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-to-construct-largest-nuclear-plant-with-chinese-design%2Famp_articleshow%2F116791515.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Traffic%20Jam%20In%20Space%2C%20ISRO%20Postpones%20SpaDeX%20Launch%20By%202%20Minutes%2C%20Now%20At%2010%20pm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20traffic%20jam%20in%20space!%20It%20has%20forced%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20to%20postpone%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%20by%20two%20minutes.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20PSLV-C60%20that%20would%20launch%20the%20SpaDeX%20mission%20or%20the%20Space%20Docking%20Experiment%20was%20to%20be%20launched%20at%209.58%20pm%2C%20but%20now%20it%20has%20been%20pushed%20to%2010%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20has%20been%20postponed%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bconjunctions%20with%20other%20satellites%20in%20the%20same%20orbit%26quot%3B%2C%20Dr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-spadex-historic-space-docking-will-put-india-in-the-big-league-isro-chief-to-ndtv-7355230%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%20Somanath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chairman%20of%20ISRO%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20ISRO%20has%20had%20to%20reschedule%20its%20launch%20due%20to%20congestion%20in%20the%20orbit%20and%20flight%20path%20of%20the%20rocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20at%20ISRO%20found%20that%20some%20satellites%20from%20the%20Starlink%20constellation%20were%20coming%20in%20the%20way.%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20about%207%2C000%20Starlink%20satellites%20in%20the%20low%20Earth%20orbit.%20This%20is%20a%20constellation%20owned%20by%20American%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20his%20company%20SpaceX.%20Starlink%20provides%20satellite-based%20broadband%20internet%20connectivity%20across%20the%20world.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20Starlink%20satellites%20is%20expected%20to%20go%20up%20to%20about%2012%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspadex-mission-how-isro-will-dock-two-satellites-in-space-7332909%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'SpaDeX'%20Mission%3A%20How%20ISRO%20Will%20Dock%20Two%20Satellites%20In%20Space%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20long%2C%20scientists%20and%20engineers%20from%20many%20space%20agencies%20have%20been%20complaining%20that%20these%20massive%20constellations%20will%20cause%20traffic%20jams%20in%20space.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20there%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20space%20debris%20in%20copious%20amounts%20that%20also%20poses%20a%20huge%20risk%20to%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20India%20had%20to%20postpone%20the%20launch%20of%20its%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20by%20a%20few%20minutes%20almost%20for%20the%20same%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20SpaDeX%20Mission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PSLV%20C-60%20mission%20has%20innovation%20written%20all%20over%20it%2C%20with%20the%20rocket%20and%20the%20satellites%20integrated%20and%20tested%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time%20at%20a%20private%20entity%2C%20Ananth%20Technologies.%20At%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Center%2C%20Sriharikota%2C%20the%20rocket%20was%20also%20assembled%20in%20a%20new%20facility.%20Further%2C%20the%20space%20docking%20experiment%20is%20a%20big%20bold%20innovative%20step%20that%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20its%20use%20in%20futuristic%20missions%20like%20Chandrayaan-4%20and%20the%20making%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Antariksha%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fsite%3Dclassic%26id%3D881840%26autostart%3Dfalse%26autoplay%3D0%26pWidth%3D650%26pHeight%3D400%26category%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20fourth%20stage%20of%20the%20PSLV%20which%20usually%20turns%20into%20space%20debris%20has%20been%20converted%20into%20an%20active%20un-crewed%20space%20laboratory.%20The%20last%20stage%20of%20the%20rocket%20has%20been%20re-purposed%20to%20become%20an%20orbital%20laboratory%20and%20from%20robotic%20experiments%20to%20growing%20cowpea%20seeds%20to%20testing%20green%20rocket%20fuel%20all%20will%20be%20tested%20on%20the%20PS4-Orbital%20Experiment%20Module%2C%20designated%20as%20POEM.%20It%20is%20carrying%2024%20experiments%20in%20space%20including%20taking%20three%20live%20biology%20experiments%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20space%20program%20is%20set%20to%20achieve%20another%20milestone%20with%20the%20Space%20Docking%20Experiment%20(SpaDeX)%20on%20its%2062nd%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%20mission.%20ISRO%20will%20attempt%20the%20docking%20and%20undocking%20of%20two%20satellites%20in%20orbit%2C%20a%20feat%20mastered%20only%20by%20Russia%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20landmark%20mission%2C%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbold%20step%26quot%3B%20by%20ISRO%20Chairman%20Dr%20S%20Somanath%2C%20will%20use%20indigenous%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20multiple%20objects%20in%20space%20that%20need%20to%20be%20brought%20together%20for%20a%20specific%20purpose%2C%20a%20mechanism%20called%20docking%20is%20required.%20Docking%20is%20the%20process%20by%20which%20two%20space%20objects%20come%20together%20and%20connect.%20This%20can%20be%20done%20using%20various%20approaches%3A%20soft%20mechanisms%2C%20hard%20mechanisms%2C%20or%20pressurized%20compartments%20for%20human%20transfer.%20For%20example%2C%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20crew%20modules%20dock%20at%20the%20station%2C%20equalize%20pressure%2C%20and%20transfer%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20capability%20is%20central%20to%20future%20ambitions%2C%20including%20India's%20Bharatiya%20Antariksha%20Station%20(a%20proposed%20Indian%20space%20station)%2C%20human%20spaceflight%20programs%2C%20and%20lunar%20sample%20return%20missions%20such%20as%20Chandrayaan-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20docking%2C%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Btarget%26quot%3B%20object%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bchaser%26quot%3B%20object.%20The%20chaser%20follows%20the%20target%2C%20comes%20into%20proximity%2C%20and%20establishes%20a%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20SpaDeX%20mission%2C%20India%20aims%20to%20join%20the%20exclusive%20club%20of%20nations%20capable%20of%20space%20docking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20success%20of%20this%20mission%20will%20position%20India%20as%20a%20major%20spacefaring%20nation%2C%20not%20just%20in%20launching%20satellites%20but%20in%20conducting%20complex%20space%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735544400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0dllv2a_spadex_625x300_30_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftraffic-jam-in-space-isro-postpones-spadex-launch-by-2-minutes-now-at-10-pm-7361891%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20a%20traffic%20jam%20in%20space!%20It%20has%20forced%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20to%20postpone%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%20by%20two%20minutes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftraffic-jam-in-space-isro-postpones-spadex-launch-by-2-minutes-now-at-10-pm-7361891%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Amsterdam-bound%20KLM%20plane%20skids%20off%20runway%20in%20Norway.%20What%20happened%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735542759000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116790877%2Cimgsize-4705583.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%