of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20year%20to%20all%20eligible%20senior%20citizens%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20financial%20background.%20Designed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(AB%20PM-JAY)%2C%20the%20card%20is%20a%20lifeline%20for%20elderly%20individuals%2C%20offering%20them%20access%20to%20quality%20healthcare%20without%20worrying%20about%20the%20cost.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-1%20wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20800px)%20100vw%2C%20800px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senior%20citizens%20deserve%20to%20enjoy%20their%20final%20innings%20without%20financial%20worries%20and%20medical%20hassles.%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22391137%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-500x313.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-768x480.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896-150x94.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391137%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenior%20citizens%20deserve%20to%20enjoy%20their%20final%20innings%20without%20financial%20worries%20and%20medical%20hassles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20crucial%20for%20those%20managing%20pre-existing%20conditions%20like%20diabetes%20or%20hypertension%2C%20which%20can%20significantly%20impact%20healthcare%20costs.%20Moreover%2C%20pre-existing%20illnesses%20can%20influence%20health%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20potentially%20resulting%20in%20higher%20costs%20or%20even%20denial%20of%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20aims%20to%20change%20the%20lives%20of%20senior%20citizens%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComprehensive%20Coverage%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cardholders%20can%20receive%20cashless%20treatment%20worth%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20annually%20at%20empanelled%20hospitals%20across%20India%2C%20covering%20an%20extensive%20range%20of%20medical%20procedures.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20the%20extensive%20list%20of%20hospitals%20that%20come%20under%20the%20card%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnha.gov.in%2Fimg%2Fresources%2FPMJAY-Hospital-List.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInclusivity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unlike%20schemes%20that%20target%20economically%20disadvantaged%20groups%2C%20this%20programme%20is%20universal%20for%20all%20citizens%20aged%2070%20and%20above%2C%20breaking%20socio-economic%20barriers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBeneficiaries%20can%20avail%20of%20treatments%20at%20any%20empanelled%20hosp